  • Interfaces 
    Interface Description
    com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.notinuse.DataFetcher
    This interface was used to fetch data from the database. It is not used in the final application. This interfaces purpose was replaced with the Middle Man.
    com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.notinuse.DataSender
    The DataSender interface was used to send data to the database. It is not used in the final application. This classes purpose was replaced with the Middle Man.
    com.example.mainapplication.ui.notifications.OnServerResponse
  • Classes 
    Class Description
    com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.mockClasses.MockDataFetcher
    com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.mockClasses.MockDataSender
    This class is a mock class for the DataSender interface. It is used for testing purposes. It is not used in the final application. This classes purpose was replaced with the Middle Man.
    com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.notinuse.ApiDataFetcher
    The purpose of this class was to fetch data from the api. It is not used in the final application. This classes purpose was replaced with the Middle Man.
    com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.notinuse.StorageAccess
    This class was used to access the storage of the app. It is not used in the final application. The Storage Access Class had to be replaced because it implemented the DataFetcher and DataSender interfaces. These interfaces were replaced with the middle man.
